es—what may be taxable in one state may be exempt in another. </p> <span class=\"text-right\" style=\"float:right\"> <a class=\"btn btn-default\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=508&url=http://addons.prestashop.com/en/billing-invoicing-prestashop-modules/5040-avalara-avatax.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=tipoftheday&utm_campaign=partenariats&utm_content=avalara%3Futm_source%3Dback-office%26utm_medium%3Dtipoftheday%26utm_campaign%3Dpartenariats%26utm_content%3Davalara\"> More information? </a> </span> </div> </section><section id=\"4_avalara\" class=\"panel\" style=\"display:none\"> <header class=\"panel-heading\"> <span class=\"icon-lightbulb\"></span> Tips of the day </header> <div class=\"panel-body\" style=\"padding:0\"> <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/production-gamification-assets/tips/avalara.png\" style=\"float:right; margin-left: 5px;\"> <img src=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/api/getAdviceImg/508.png\"/> <p> <b>How can one zip code be miles apart when dealing with taxes?</b> </p> <p> A single ZIP code can have multiple tax rates. </p> <span class=\"text-right\" style=\"float:right\"> <a class=\"btn btn-default\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=508&url=http://addons.prestashop.com/en/billing-invoicing-prestashop-modules/5040-avalara-avatax.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=tipoftheday&utm_campaign=partenariats&utm_content=avalara%3Futm_source%3Dback-office%26utm_medium%3Dtipoftheday%26utm_campaign%3Dpartenariats%26utm_content%3Davalara\"> More information? </a> </span> </div> </section><section id=\"5_avalara\" class=\"panel\" style=\"display:none\"> <header class=\"panel-heading\"> <span class=\"icon-lightbulb\"></span> Tips of the day </header> <div class=\"panel-body\" style=\"padding:0\"> <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/production-gamification-assets/tips/avalara.png\" style=\"float:right; margin-left: 5px;\"> <img src=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/api/getAdviceImg/508.png\"/> <p> <b>Are your customers’ tax exempt status updated?</b> </p> <p> Check that customers’ tax exempt status is updated and agrees with the term of their exemption certificate on file. </p> <span class=\"text-right\" style=\"float:right\"> <a class=\"btn btn-default\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=508&url=http://addons.prestashop.com/en/billing-invoicing-prestashop-modules/5040-avalara-avatax.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=tipoftheday&utm_campaign=partenariats&utm_content=avalara%3Futm_source%3Dback-office%26utm_medium%3Dtipoftheday%26utm_campaign%3Dpartenariats%26utm_content%3Davalara\"> More information? </a> </span> </div> </section><section id=\"6_avalara\" class=\"panel\" style=\"display:none\"> <header class=\"panel-heading\"> <span class=\"icon-lightbulb\"></span> Tips of the day </header> <div class=\"panel-body\" style=\"padding:0\"> <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/production-gamification-assets/tips/avalara.png\" style=\"float:right; margin-left: 5px;\"> <img src=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/api/getAdviceImg/508.png\"/> <p> <b>What’s the average price to manage a sales tax audit?</b> </p> <p> It costs over $96k on average to manage a sales tax audit. </p> <span class=\"text-right\" style=\"float:right\"> <a class=\"btn btn-default\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=508&url=http://addons.prestashop.com/en/billing-invoicing-prestashop-modules/5040-avalara-avatax.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=tipoftheday&utm_campaign=partenariats&utm_content=avalara%3Futm_source%3Dback-office%26utm_medium%3Dtipoftheday%26utm_campaign%3Dpartenariats%26utm_content%3Davalara\"> More information? </a> </span> </div> </section><section id=\"7_avalara\" class=\"panel\" st